De_dustmtg 2007 by DDoS

*********************************** 
A Counter-strike source map
*********************************** 
TITLE: de_dustmtg
AUTHOR: DDoS
E-MAIL: nathanael@hotmail.co.uk
FILENAME: de_dustmtg.bsp / de_dustmtg.nav
FILESIZE: 4.38mb zipped
DATE RELEASED: 7th may 2007

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Please extract to C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\yourusername\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps. 

DESCRIPTION: de_dustmtg is a counter-strike source bomb diffusal map based losely around de_dust2. It is best suited to 5v5 matches, but I have 
added spawn points for upto 30 players.

BUGS: None?

COMMENTS: Oh not another dust map I hear you say! well the truth is there are very few good ones and the texture set is both resource cheap and 
well suited to spotting players from a long way off. The map is free to use, and circulate but please give me credit:) Also the name mtg is of my
 clan -> mtgeurope.com for more info.

Big thanks to my wife for her patience and understanding:) 

email me with any feedback/bugs please:)
